M code, we conclude that the model would benefit from NR simulations\nspecifically targeted at improving the postmerger-ringdown phenomenological\nfits for mass ratios $\\gtrsim 8$ and spins $\\gtrsim 0.8$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Mar 2017 16:03:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-01"}
