n while the Boomerang's\nprimary was an RGB or early-AGB star, with the companion finally merging into\nthe primary's core, and ejecting the primary's envelope that now forms the\nultra-cold outflow.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Mar 2017 19:11:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 May 2017 02:20:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-14"}
