 can increase the sensitivity of the experiment by up to 25\\%.\nSuch a reduction of the systematic errors is crucial for determining the\noscillation parameters with greater significance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Mar 2017 10:44:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Oct 2017 08:55:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-25"}
